OL,3,CKidnapped model Chloe Ayling hopes new
OL,4,CTV drama of her ordeal will stop
OL,5,Cdoubters
OL,7,FTwo men were jailed for Ms Ayling's
OL,8,Fkidnap, but she was accused of faking
OL,9,Fher ordeal and of being involved in a
OL,10,F"publicity stunt". These accusations
OL,11,Fare still being made online today.
OL,13,FMs Ayling hopes a new six-part drama
OL,14,Fbased on her ordeal will encourage
OL,15,Fpeople to "keep an open mind before
OL,16,Fjumping to conclusions".
