OL,3,CKidnapped model Chloe Ayling hopes new
OL,4,CTV drama of her ordeal will stop
OL,5,Cdoubters
OL,7,FThe BBC series, Kidnapped: The Chloe
OL,8,FAyling Story, is based on her
OL,9,Fkidnapping and time in captivity, as
OL,10,Fwell as the subsequent court case that
OL,11,Fput the perpetrators in prison.
OL,13,F"I hope it encourages people not to
OL,14,Fdoubt victims based on the way they
OL,15,Freact to a traumatic experience, based
OL,16,Fon the way they dress, their job or
OL,17,Fwhat they did to survive," Ms Ayling
OL,18,Fsaid ahead of the launch of the series.
