OL,3,CKidnapped model Chloe Ayling hopes new
OL,4,CTV drama of her ordeal will stop
OL,5,Cdoubters
OL,7,FMs Ayling, aged 20 at the time, was
OL,8,Fdrugged, bundled into a suitcase and
OL,9,Fabducted after arriving at a Milan
OL,10,Faddress for a modelling job. She was
OL,11,Fheld in a farmhouse near Turin while a
OL,12,F300,000 euro (#265,000) ransom was
OL,13,Fdemanded.
OL,15,FShe was released six days later at the
OL,16,FBritish Consulate in Milan.
