OL,3,CKidnapped model Chloe Ayling hopes new
OL,4,CTV drama of her ordeal will stop
OL,5,Cdoubters
OL,7,FPolish national Lukasz Herba and his
OL,8,Fbrother, Michal Herba, were
OL,9,Fsubsequently jailed for 16 years and
OL,10,Fnine months after an Italian court
OL,11,Fconvicted them of kidnapping Ms Ayling.
OL,13,F"I feared for my life second by
OL,14,Fsecond, minute by minute, hour by
OL,15,Fhour," Ms Ayling said in a press
OL,16,Fconference in 2017 following the
OL,17,Fkidnapping.
