OL,4,CTV drama of her ordeal will stop
OL,5,Cdoubters
OL,7,FMs Ayling hopes the new drama will
OL,8,Fallow the public to view the story
OL,9,Ffrom her perspective as she feels many
OL,10,Fkey aspects were not fully revealed at
OL,11,Fthe time, including some details about
OL,12,Fthe court case.
OL,14,F"It's important for me that people can
OL,15,Fnow see all of those key details based
OL,16,Fon years of extensive research and not
OL,17,Fa warped version of the truth," she
OL,18,Fsaid.
