OL,5,Cdoubters
OL,7,FMs Ayling opened up about her
OL,8,Fkidnapping after entering the
OL,9,FCelebrity Big Brother house in 2018
OL,10,Fwhere she discussed how she tried to
OL,11,Fconvince her captor to let her go.
OL,13,F"He made it out to me it was a massive
OL,14,Forganisation and he wanted to save me
OL,15,Fbut he couldn't because there were so
OL,16,Fmany people behind it," Ms Ayling told
OL,17,FUS reality star Natalie Nunn.
